  "variable_placeholders": "Victorian brass pressure gauge authored facing south (+Z), with its wall contact at z=0. The static group contains the mounting rose, terminal manifold, stepped brass case, bezel, dial, and fixed hub. Rotate the needle group around local Z at origin [8,9,5.3]. Suggested runtime sweep: -135 degrees at zero pressure to +135 degrees at burst pressure. frequency_slots contains the two future Redstone Link frequency item surfaces. The included animation is preview-only.",
